															<div class="panel panel-default">
																<div class="panel-heading">
																	<h4 class="panel-title">
																		<a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse23">Tracking deals in a sales pipeline</a>
																	</h4>
																</div>
																<div id="collapse23" class="panel-collapse collapse">
																	<div class="panel-body">
																		A sales pipeline is a set of steps you need to take in order to close a Deal (the steps are called Pipeline Stages in Pipedrive and can be customized to fit your workflow). Having a sales pipeline helps you visualize the process of getting a Deal won and also gets the entire team on the same page so everyone knows what the process is like. In pipeline99 this concept is made very visual, the steps are displayed from left to right and you can drag your Deals forward through the pipeline as progress is made
																	</div>
